    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "College has good ground with so many trees, their is greenery all around which I feel is good for the students and teachers as nature is absolute treat to eye in so much pressure of studies and teachings.",
          "name": "Ramsha Shamim",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Fees is reasonable, they offer placement opportunities as well. Moreover students can enjoy scholarship benefits",
          "name": "Ramsha Shamim",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Teachers are well educated and has good communication skills.",
          "name": "Ramsha Shamim",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Talking about the science branch it's worth to study there .They provide great knowledge and practical experiences . Well educated teachers and great learning experience.",
          "name": "Aishanya Tripathi",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Also they conduct so many seminar in the auditorium which is very beautiful and informative .",
          "name": "Aishanya Tripathi",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Everything related to study is super nice there in a very good budget also you can avail your scholarship which compensates all the fees",
          "name": "Aishanya Tripathi",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Course Curriculum is good. I feel it is designed after thorough discussion.",
          "name": "Ujjwal Monga",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Faculty is very supportive and active in helping the students.",
          "name": "Ujjwal Monga",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Classes are held regularly and there is a healthy studious atmosphere.",
          "name": "Ujjwal Monga",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is one table tennis room where we play tt for relaxation.",
          "name": "Chaitanya Singh Yadav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Classes are not scheduled properly, many time one subject class overlap the other.",
          "name": "Ramsha Shamim",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Classes are not well organised and cleaned, clean class means better concentration this is what I feel.",
          "name": "Ramsha Shamim",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "College have garden also but no any care in daily routine.",
          "name": "Shikha Gautam",
          "course_tag_name": "D.El.Ed."
        },
        {
          "text": "College close time schedule is not fix for every classes.some classes close in the evening",
          "name": "Shikha Gautam",
          "course_tag_name": "D.El.Ed."
        },
        {
          "text": "Some days gallery area around campus is dirty",
          "name": "Chaitanya Singh Yadav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Timings can be well planned",
          "name": "Chaitanya Singh Yadav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is no hostel facility for students",
          "name": "Chaitanya Singh Yadav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "They don't have any canteen, which is again something which I dislike about my college, every college should have canteen.",
          "name": "Ramsha Shamim",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "I also liked the college schedule a little bit because classes of some subjects were conducted at the same time.",
          "name": "Rachit Patel",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "I wish everyone was allowed inside library.",
          "name": "Anushka",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        }
      ]
    },
